{"alignment_id": "shijing__song-chengong-007__001__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sbe-v3-1879", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "song-chengong-007", "alignment_type": "exact_or_near_exact", "confidence": 0.99, "order": 1, "section_unit": "poem", "segment_type": "stanza", "alignment_granularity": "stanza", "is_coarse_alignment": false, "coarse_alignment_reason": null, "source_segment_count": 1, "target_segment_count": 1, "chinese_ref": "詩經·頌·臣工之什·007.1", "chinese_text": "有來雝雝，至止肅肅。相維辟公，天子穆穆。於薦廣牡，相予肆祀。", "translation_ref": "雝.1", "translation_text": "They come full of harmony;\nThey are here in all gravity;—\nThe\nprinces assisting,\nWhile the Son of Heaven looks profound."}
{"alignment_id": "shijing__song-chengong-007__002__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sbe-v3-1879", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "song-chengong-007", "alignment_type": "exact_or_near_exact", "confidence": 0.99, "order": 2, "section_unit": "poem", "segment_type": "stanza", "alignment_granularity": "stanza", "is_coarse_alignment": false, "coarse_alignment_reason": null, "source_segment_count": 1, "target_segment_count": 1, "chinese_ref": "詩經·頌·臣工之什·007.2", "chinese_text": "假哉皇考，綏予孝子。宣哲維人，文武維后。燕及皇天，克昌厥後。", "translation_ref": "雝.2", "translation_text": "(He says), 'While I present (this) noble bull,\nAnd they assist me in setting forth the sacrifice,\nO great and august Father,\nComfort me, your filial son."}
{"alignment_id": "shijing__song-chengong-007__003__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sbe-v3-1879", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "song-chengong-007", "alignment_type": "exact_or_near_exact", "confidence": 0.99, "order": 3, "section_unit": "poem", "segment_type": "stanza", "alignment_granularity": "stanza", "is_coarse_alignment": false, "coarse_alignment_reason": null, "source_segment_count": 1, "target_segment_count": 1, "chinese_ref": "詩經·頌·臣工之什·007.3", "chinese_text": "綏我眉壽，介以繁祉。既右烈考，亦右文母。", "translation_ref": "雝.3", "translation_text": "'With penetrating wisdom thou didst play the man,\nA sovereign with the gifts both of peace and war,\nGiving rest even to great Heaven,\nAnd ensuring prosperity to thy descendants."}
